nteer group  st air commando group  after discharge  notes  references  external links early lifeedit he was born in york nebraska his family moved to red cloud from hooper nebraska in  when his father earl w smith was hired as superintendent of schools he graduated red cloud high school in  smith attended the university of nebraska before joining the us army air corps in  midway through his senior year flight trainingedit he received his primary flight training at the allan hancock college of aeronautics at santa maria california during his training he was given a couple of check rides with robert l scott who on may   flew as smiths wingman on scotts first combat mission in china smith completed basic training with class c at randolph field texas and advanced training at brooks field texas he was commissioned a second lieutenant in june  and returned to randolph field where his first assignment was as a basic flight instructor american volunteer groupedit smith resigned his commission in july  in order to join colonel claire lee chennaults american volunteer group avg as a soldier of fortune with the nationalist chinese air force the flying tigers as they were soon to be called were in burma training in curtiss ps actually hawk model as or as the british called them tomahawks when pearl harbor was attacked on december   december  on their side of the international dateline rt smith sometimes called tadpole after david lee tex hill supplied the answer to a question someone posed to smith “what’s the ‘t’ stand for” saw his first combat action over rangoon on december   when he was credited with shooting down  mitsubishi ki sally bombers followed on christmas day with credit for two more sally bombers and a fighter promoted to flight leader in the third pursuit squadron hells angels smith was credited with shooting down a total of  japanese planes and was twice decorated by the chinese government the avg continued to fight throughout burma and southwest china until it was officially disbanded on july   st air commando groupedit st air commando group bomber section commander rt smith and cocommanders john alison and phil cochran in front of rt smiths bh barbie iii at hailkandi india in march  smith returned to the united states on the usat mariposa along with  other avg pilots and ground personnel prior to being drafted as a private in december  smith served as the technical advisor on the sky’s the limit directed by eh griffith and starring fred astaire and joan leslie the side of the p astaire is flying at the beginning of the movie has a sitting hell’s angel of the avg’s third squadron that was on the side of smith’s p  smith was quickly recommissioned as a us air corps second lieutenant and promoted to major the next month for the next few months as commanding officer of the  fighter squadron  fighter group at glendale california and paine field everett washington he trained replacement pilots using lockheed p lightning fighter aircraft smith married barbara bradford in june  adopting her son brad from a previous marriage to vaudeville performer george mann shortly after being appointed commanding officer of the th fighter group in september  he volunteered to return to the chinaindiaburma theater with the st air commando group flying occasional p mustang missions and commanding that groups b mitchell squadron in support of british general orde wingates troops working out of india and moving behind japanese lines in burma now myanmar one story is told of when smith was flying alone in his p named barbie after his wife and saw a crowd gathered around a jeep on the flying field someone was making a speech and smith assumed it was phil cochran cocommander with john alison of the st air commando group he put his p into a dive and buzzed the speaker nearly taking his hat off at over  miles an hour it was only after smith landed that he learned the speaker was lord louis mountbatten supreme allied commander southeast asia lord mountbatten was not angry at smith but was angry at his aide for having him make a speech on an active flying field smith rt according to chuck baisden for round trip while in the st air commando group was promoted to lieutenant colonel in march  flew  combat missions over burma and was awarded the air medal distinguished flying cross and silver star after dischargeedit painting of curtiss p warhawk in the republic of china air force autographed by rt smith hells angels flying tigers in formation over china  photo and autograph by rt smith smith returned to the united states in the late spring of  and was assigned as director of flying training with the st army air force base unit at van nuys california a p training base the base operations officer at the time was major barry goldwater he resigned from the air corps at the conclusion of world war ii and bought a home in the san fernando valley in southern california across from the los angeles river when it was actually a river instead of the concrete channel it is today after flying dcs and constellations between los angeles and kansas city for a year and a half with transworld airlines twa he wrote radio scripts for the hopalong cassidy western adventure show lum and abner the phil harrisalice faye show and the clyde beatty show he also wrote the screenplay with frank taussig for the  movie perils of the jungle starring clyde beatty smith was coowner of a toy manufacturing company smithmiller developed and sold a product for conditioning automobile convertible tops top secret and worked for roy weatherby as a sales manager for weatherbys inc r t and barbara smith were divorced in  about this time smith joined lockheed aircraft corporation as a technical writer working his way up through the organization first as a military sales representative for the f starfighter and later to open and manage a new corporate office for lockheed in newport news virginia smith served at the rank of lieutenant colonel in the air force reserve from  to  smith married ronni burkett in july  during the late s he joined the flying tiger line first as vice president for industrial affairs in washington dc and later as vice president for the far east headquartered in tokyo he left the flying tiger line and tokyo in the early s to live and work in palm springs california r t and ronni smith were divorced in the mids he returned to the san fernando valley where he wrote and published tale of a tiger based on facsimiles of his original diary entries and several articles for air classics he also established a mailorder business selling his book and color photographs he shot while he was in the avg and st air commando group including this often reproduced formation shot of the rd squadron hells angels taken on may   near the salween river along the chinaburma border he died at age  the number he had selected for his first p in the avg of lung cancer on august   smith was survived by his sister june who died in  three sons bradford robert and william and three grandchildren william reed smith is named in honor of his good friend bill reed who died in december  while serving with the chineseamerican composite wing notesedit  burke kate march   york native was a flying tiger york timesnews   a b biography of rt smith on flying tigers association website retrieved    smith rt  tale of a tiger van nuys ca tiger originals p  isbn    scott jr robert l  god is my copilot garden city ny blue ribbon books p    chadwick major bf october   lets get acquainted the military service news   ford daniel  flying tigers claire chennault and his american volunteers new york harper collins p  isbn    rossi jr  the flying tigers – american volunteer group – chinese air force avg   flying tigers in city tell of epic campaign new york herald tribune september    accessdate requires url help  flying tiger back in army as private los angeles examiner december    accessdate requires url help  the skys the limit internet movie database