tions corporate governance matters and leadership experience qualifying him to serve on fultons board of directors source fulton financial corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view r scott smith jrs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like r scott smith jr more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in r scott smith jrs network and community follow changes in r scott smith jrs employment and moneyinmotion connect with r scott smith jr through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example r scott smith jr r scott smith jrs connections  sign up now to view r scott smith jrs  connections » james e shreiner former senior executive vice president fulton financial corporation meg r mueller senior executive vice president and chief credit officer fulton financial corporation curtis j myers senior executive vice president president and chief operating officer fulton bank na fulton financial corporation craig h hill former senior executive vice presidenthuman resources corporate communications and administrative services fulton financial corporation craig a roda senior executive vice president community banking chairman and chief executive officer fulton bank na fulton financial corporation charles j nugent former senior executive vice president and chief financial officer fulton financial corporation philmer h rohrbaugh senior executive vice president chief operating officer and interim chief financial officer fulton financial corporation dana a chryst former board member fulton financial corporation patrick j freer board member fulton financial corporation george w hodges chairman of the board the york water company popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla daniel a de